TFTs New Set 16: Lore & Legends

Lore & Legends is the latest Set for Teamfight Tactics, sending players through the history of Runeterra's world and limitless archives of knowledge with 24+ four & five-cost champions!
The new Set will be on PBE soon!

Lore & Legends

100 Champions - NEW Mechanic, Augments, Items, Cosmetics, and more.

With Set 16 - Lore & Legends, youll have a mechanic called Unlockables that will give you access to 40 more champions! You will be able to Unlock champions once you fullfilled their Unlock Condition and they will stay unlocked for the rest of your game!

Ionia

Each game, they walk a different path.

  • Path of Spirit: Ionians gain bonus HP. When one casts, they gain stacking AD and AP
  • Path of Generosity: Every third takedown Ionians participate in grants 1 gold. Ionians gain AD and AP, increased by 1% for every gold earned this way.
  • Path of Enlightenment: Ionians gain AD and AP plus more based on your level. After each player combat, gain XP.
  • Path of Transcendence: Ionians gain bonus Health and deal bonus magic damage. These effects increase if theyre three-starred.
  • Path of Precision: Ionian abilities can critically strike and they gain Critical Strike Chance. Whenever an Ionian casts, Ionian units gain stacking AD and AP.

Other Set 16 Changes

Unlockables Rules & Conditions

Unlockables have specific Unlock Rules & Conditions

  • Your first copy of an Unlockable champion is always guaranteed in your next shop (on the rightest spot) - after you met the Unlock condition
  • Unlockable champions follow the standard bag-size and can be contested
  • If you don't buy/play Unlockable champions - they will have less odds appearing in your shop
